sources.description:
The Devil's Mistress PART ONE: Set during the English Civil War, this miniseries explores a country in crisis through the eyes of Angelica Fanshawe—from the abandonment of her loyalty to the Royal Family to her destitute existence as a prostitute to her position as the intimate confidante of the notorious Oliver Cromwell.

Watch Part 2: https://youtu.be/IE4-maKPnIM

Starring: 
Dominic West (The Crown)
Michael Fassbender
John Simm
Jeremy Crutchley
Peter Capaldi (Dr. Who)
Tom Goodman-Hill
Andrea Riseborough

2008
Directed by Marc Munden
